It stars Vijay Sethupathi, Gayathrie Shankar, Vigneshwaran Palanisamy, Bagavathi Perumal and Rajkumar, thus marking the acting debut for Rajkumar, Vigneshwaran and Bagavathi. Govindaraj. The film is a sequel to K.G.F: Chapter 1, which was released in 2018. Yash is reprising his lead role from the first film and Hindi actor Sanjay Dutt will star as the antagonist, marking his debut in Kannada.
